25:24.760 --> 25:27.354
An individual,
Suspect Number 1,

25:27.440 --> 25:29.158
uh, now dead, we know.

25:29.240 --> 25:31.037
Fuckin' A!

25:31.120 --> 25:33.076
- Oh, my God!
- You son of a bitch!

25:34.480 --> 25:36.914
Fuckin' kill
that other son of a bitch, too!

26:06.760 --> 26:10.196
Jeffrey, I just met Carlos.

26:12.240 --> 26:14.117
He's the guy
who saved your life.

26:28.640 --> 26:30.551
Would you like a coffee?

26:30.640 --> 26:32.870
I brought some...
I've got some... got some coffees.

26:36.520 --> 26:38.476
