I'm supposed to do.

26:42.680 --> 26:44.511
I think everyone
in that hospital

26:44.600 --> 26:46.477
is thinking that same thing.

26:47.560 --> 26:48.595
Yeah.

26:53.040 --> 26:55.315
We broke up about a month ago,
me and Jeff.

26:59.200 --> 27:02.397
It's not the first time...
we usually get back together.

27:06.000 --> 27:07.433
Not this time?

27:10.200 --> 27:12.430
Doesn't show up
for anything.

27:12.520 --> 27:14.636
He's always late.

27:14.720 --> 27:17.792
You know, he... he never wants
to leave his apartment.

27:17.880 --> 27:19.472
I'm just fed up with it.

27:21.800 --> 27:23.552
And then he shows up.

27:38.120 --> 27:40.793
Sounded like
multiple assault rifle shots to me.

27:40.880 --> 27:43.314
8:15 p.m.,
a person is cornered

27:43.400 --> 27:45.311
on a boat in a yard
in Watertown.

27:45.400 --> 27:46.936
A suspect in the boat.

27:46.960 --> 27:48.016
Hundreds of law enforcement...

27:48.040 --> 27:49.598
- Hi.
- Hi.

27:49.680 --> 27:50.856
Jeff, how you doin'?

27:50.880 --> 27:52.560
So, Jeff, we have to do

27:52.600 --> 27:53.953
the first dressing change today.

27:54.040 --> 27:55.792
Okay, we're gonna take
these bandages off.

27:58.000 --> 27:59.592
