28:25.800 --> 28:27.995
All righty.
I'm gonna just lift ya up.

28:28.080 --> 28:29.136
You're gonna feel my hands.

28:29.160 --> 28:30.309
I'm sorry, hon.

28:33.280 --> 28:34.736
So I'm just taking the tape off,

28:34.760 --> 28:37.399
