any sharp pains or anything,

28:42.320 --> 28:44.834
please let me know.

28:44.920 --> 28:46.296
All right,
you're gonna feel my hands.

28:46.320 --> 28:48.880
Tell me if you're ready.
Did that kick in yet?

28:48.960 --> 28:50.632
- Doing okay?
- Yeah, yeah.

28:50.720 --> 28:52.119
All right.

28:54.480 --> 28:56.198
Almost done with the gauze.

28:57.720 --> 28:59.392
Fuck.

28:59.480 --> 29:00.549
You okay?

