Yeah.

29:03.000 --> 29:05.230
You let us know
if you need a break, okay?

29:07.840 --> 29:09.319
You're okay.

29:09.400 --> 29:10.753
Don't look at 'em.

29:10.840 --> 29:11.989
I'm not lookin' at 'em.

29:12.080 --> 29:13.216
Okay, now
this might be a little sticky.

29:13.240 --> 29:14.514
- Looking at you.
- God!

29:14.600 --> 29:15.896
Doin' great. Doin' great.

29:15.920 --> 29:18.070
You're doin' awesome.

29:18.160 --> 29:20.799
Okay, the dressing's off.
We'll give you a minute.

29:22.160 --> 29:24.276
- Nice little breaths.
- Good job.

29:24.360 --> 29:26.271
In your nose,
out your mouth.

29:26.360 --> 29:27.576
You're doing so great.

29:27.600 --> 29:28.919
That was the worst.

29:29.000 --> 29:30.520
