Now, same thing,
dried blood, big pull.

30:15.320 --> 30:16.696
- One, two, three.
- One, two, three.

30:16.720 --> 30:19.871
That's it, that's it.

30:19.960 --> 30:21.279
Right here.

30:30.240 --> 30:31.275
Hey.

30:34.760 --> 30:35.829
Hey.

30:37.080 --> 30:38.195
